flowRoot.flowPara: With over a decade in the education industry from teaching through to management, purchasing, education sales, curriculum writing and consulting, publishing, library management and sales, digital publishing and integration, and education software, I am passionately dedicated to improving the education space, developing the tools educators and students actually need to support and improve their learning experience. And I always ensure my team has enough chocolate and cake to make them productive!
